{"id": 2206, "genre": 1000, "title": "关于“委婉说话”这件事，你都经历过哪些困扰？", "description": "人们对“什么情况下该用什么语气”的理解有偏差的时候，问题就来了。欢迎在评论区补充你的困扰。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 7697, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180302153522ajwxtZ9KhvVcD3H4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-04T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3813, "title": "关于“委婉说话”这件事，你都经历过哪些困扰？", "content": "“委婉说话”这件事给你带来过哪些困扰？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 268365, "content": "同事同学说我作品“还行”，交上去的结局却是被打回", "image": "img/option/option/20180304223359wZTMf4GpJAnN2rEi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268367, "content": "老板皱眉说“我建议你稍微改改”，后来知道其实需要大改", "image": "img/option/option/20180304223425B5WAJfOH9KciRD7m.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268368, "content": "聊天不知道说啥的时候也要发个表情，经常来回两三轮", "image": "img/option/option/20180304223503ndcSRrCItfjLJMbq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268369, "content": "被问“这个好不好看”时敷衍说好，后来收到了这个礼物", "image": "img/option/option/20180304223610GyJ0l9FB1qWOXski.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268370, "content": "被问“介意我抽烟吗”之类问题，心里介意又不敢明说", "image": "img/option/option/20180304223654ORcgqFz4lYSwUN0M.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268371, "content": "和不太熟的朋友开玩笑，结果被人当成认真的", "image": "img/option/option/20180304223819UzOQ9f8SYVkR14WD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268373, "content": "不想参加聚会只会说“天气不太好吧”，别人根本 get 不到", "image": "img/option/option/20180304224018f9TUsphzyRvNMj7E.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 268374, "content": "遇到推销不好意思强硬拒绝，被对方一直纠缠", "image": "img/option/option/20180304223926NHrLu7bfTR9svoSA.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}